Output .tmp/pi-demo/pi-demo-technical.mp4

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set Padding 18
Set TypingSpeed 32ms
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Hide
Type "bun run scripts/pi-demo/launch.ts --prepared"
Enter
Sleep 7s
Show

Type "Remember that I understand coding concepts best through cooking metaphors"
Enter
Sleep 7s

Type "Find my explanation preferences"
Enter
Sleep 7s

Ctrl+O
Sleep 5s

Ctrl+O
Type "/quit"
Enter
Sleep 2s
